# How To Tag A Zettel

<!TODO keep adding to the Zettelkast tagging specification>

Tags must be of the form `+FooBarBaz` and follow the conventions for tagging
different types of notes.

Each note of a given type should contain the associated tags:

## Courses

+CourseNotes  - Notes from a course
+CourseIndex  - The index page for a course
+<CourseName> - The name of the particular course

## Bibliographical entries

+Bibliography   - For a bibliographical note
+WebResource    - To specify an online bibliographical note
+Book           - To specify a literary bibliographical note
+<ResourceName> - The name of the resource (book title or domain name)

## Code snippets

+<Language>     - The name of the programming language
+<Topic>        - The particular topic the snippet pertains to

